{"tid":985321,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日見工...","createTime":"2019-01-17T13:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T14:11:34.000Z","uid":135240,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b42ab7cb15161aaeeb4cf1becf85813d2d0d6da9","tid":985321,"uid":135240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:08:32.000Z","msg":"類似一間startup<br />\n同老細同另一個員工傾咗好多關於開發緊嘅野<br />\n個老細話：你諗到idea就話我知啦，到時我就請你<br />\n而職位係part-time嘅assistant，連人工都未傾<br />\n<br />\n引發咗我一連串嘅思考<br />\n<br />\n到底，<br />\n比我諗到解決你諗咗幾年嘅問題我就係老細啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n定<br />\n老細請你返黎係解決問題，唔係製造問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪我要解決嘅事跨越咗我嘅職位能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋順帶一問<br />\n為咗搵經驗係咪預咗比人揸壓<br />\n<br />\n利申：純思考，非指責今日情況"},{"pid":"97f6dd08e3bcd920d84125c3cf2d5e1a692b90d2","tid":985321,"uid":170252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:18:52.000Z","msg":"如果俾我霖到老細要解決既問題，不如自己開公司賣個solution俾老細rather than個時先做佢員工"},{"pid":"401ab8d4479a27b463812dc60c28bfe970f335ed","tid":985321,"uid":221490,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗到都唔話你知啦又未請<br />\n完全係偷橋"},{"pid":"0eaa214d56a25716a6a40d7c06a690a9cb28f739","tid":985321,"uid":135240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97f6dd08e3bcd920d84125c3cf2d5e1a692b90d2","tid":985321,"uid":170252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:18:52.000Z","msg":"如果俾我霖到老細要解決既問題，不如自己開公司賣個solution俾老細rather than個時先做佢員工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T13:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁係咪冇乜經驗就要被擠壓"},{"pid":"aa92d048d05a31d3dab6699625fec7d045b49b69","tid":985321,"uid":135240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"401ab8d4479a27b463812dc60c28bfe970f335ed","tid":985321